<p>The <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] tex=
t-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848=
]/30">MistralDetector</code> class serves as the primary API for making pre=
dictions with trained GigaCheck models. It abstracts the complexity of mode=
l loading, input preparation, and output parsing, providing a consistent in=
terface regardless of whether the model performs document-level classificat=
ion or fine-grained interval detection.</p>
<p><strong>Key responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Load pretrained models from checkpoint paths</li>
<li>Tokenize input text with proper length handling</li>
<li>Execute forward passes through the model</li>
<li>Parse and format prediction outputs</li>
<li>Merge overlapping intervals for detection tasks</li>
</ul>
